Story_Texts.SourceString: We made it to Leafy Treeland. There are lots of leaves. And trees.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: We made it to Leafy Treeland. There are lots of leaves. And trees.

Story_Texts.SourceString: Be careful, this isn’t like the Forest of Mixed Emotions.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Be careful, this isn’t like the Forest of Mixed Emotions.

Story_Texts.SourceString: The ancients planted the first giant Elden Athar trees here.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: The ancients planted the first giant Elden Athar trees here.

Story_Texts.SourceString: These forests have become home to fierce beasts.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: These forests have become home to fierce beasts.

Story_Texts.SourceString: Pshhh… I'm not worried about pruning some plants!
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Pshhh… I'm not worried about pruning some plants!

Story_Texts.SourceString: You may change your mind soon, Breaker. I am Kiyu.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: You may change your mind soon, Breaker. I am Kiyu.

Story_Texts.SourceString: If you seek to cleanse Zerath’s corruption, then I will be your guide.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: If you seek to cleanse Zerath’s corruption, then I will be your guide.

Story_Texts.SourceString: It doesn't sound like we have a choice. Lead the way, Kiyu.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: It doesn't sound like we have a choice. Lead the way, Kiyu.
